{
  "stem": "18813.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 90.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to put dates or what because I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Untersturmfuhrer of Plaszow was Amon 'Go-oth.'",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goeth.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goeth.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have his picture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [SIGHS] if I would meet him, I wouldn't be talking to you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever met him, that was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very-- no, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a lucky one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If he was-- if he had to pass by us-- as a matter of fact, he hanged two of my good friends, two boys who had started to run away from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Up And we had to pass by to see how they're hanging.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was Oneg Fuchs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other one, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one I remember for sure-- beautiful two boys, just beautiful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're each about 17, 18-- gorgeous boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that's-- I don't know we knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew about Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were fasting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know [LAUGHS] with what-- we had enough to fast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we-- but we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how that we find out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Brunnlitz with Schindler-- Schindler's List.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all went-- not to Brunnlitz, to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz, we were about three and a half weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went-- Schindler took me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I can't-- I cannot tell you exactly how long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working from the Plaszow and from Emalia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that had nothing to do because that was a list what they made for him, who is going, who is not going.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was lucky enough that I went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I told you before, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My girlfriend said, do you know-- Marcel Goldberg was his name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ask him to put-- that's-- I heard it's very good, which she didn't know what she was talking.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
